inlineEdit.helpText:
Hint: specifies a short hint that describes the expected value, the hint is only displayed if no value is present.
Value: specifies the value

widgets.name: <table>
widgets.allowedChild: html.tbody, html.thead, html.tfoot, html.tr, html.caption, html.colgroup

widgets.name: <tbody>
widgets.description: Groups the body content in an HTML table

widgets.name: <td>
widgets.description: Defines a standard cell in an HTML table

widgets.name: <tfoot>
widgets.description: Groups footer content in an HTML table

widgets.name: <th>
widgets.description: Defines a header cell in an HTML table

widgets.name: <thead>
widgets.description: Groups header content in an HTML table

widgets.name: <tr>
widgets.description: Defines a row in an HTML table

widgets.name: <caption>
widgets.description: Defines a caption for a table

widgets.name: <col>
widgets.description: Specifies column properties for each column within a <colgroup> element

widgets.name: <colgroup>
widgets.description: Specifies a group of one or more columns in a table for formatting
